name: Jennifer Opal - Telling your story by The Baby Developer Show
summary:
In this episode, Nathaniel chats with Jennifer about her journey into tech and she shares her experiences navigating learning difficulties, Networking and building up a profile online.
This episode was supported by Twilio TV. Check out the Twilio Unplugged series here: twil.io/unplugged
